# Contributing Guide

Thank you for considering contributing to this repository!

## How to Contribute

1. Fork the repo and create your branch from `main`.
2. Ensure your changes pass CI and are linted.
3. Reference an issue in your PR using `#<issue-number>`.
4. If modifying workflows, test with dry-runs or forked repos.

## Code of Conduct

This project follows a standard Contributor Covenant.
